      • paintComponent

        public void paintComponent(java.awt.Graphics tablet)
        Paints this fridge on the screen and asks all the magnets on this fridge to draw themselves Steps: 1. Set the tablet's color to white using the tablet's setColor method. 2. Fill the tablet using the tablet's fillRect method. 3. For every magnet on the fridge, redraw the magnet using the magnet's draw method.
